"title": "4284: sun",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "4284: sun",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>Created as a source of light and heat and an indicator of time and direction. The sun is also used as a metaphor for the splendour and light of God himself and the righteousness of his people.</p>\n<h2>Natural functions of the sun</h2>\n<h3>A source of light</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen1:16-Gen1:18\">GEN 1:16–1:18</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps136:7-Ps136:8\">PSA 136:7–136:8</a></p>\n<h3>A marker of time</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen1:14\">GEN 1:14</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen29:7\">GEN 29:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod22:26\">EXO 22:26</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg9:33\">JDG 9:33</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam11:9\">1SA 11:9</a></p>\n<h3>An indicator of direction</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num21:11\">NUM 21:11</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod27:13\">EXO 27:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut11:30\">DEU 11:30</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Josh19:12\">JOS 19:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps113:3\">PSA 113:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa45:6\">ISA 45:6</a></p>\n<h3>A blessing, necessary for life</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eccl11:7\">ECC 11:7</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut33:13-Deut33:14\">DEU 33:13–33:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job8:16\">JOB 8:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt5:45\">MAT 5:45</a></p>\n<h3>The scorching heat causing discomfort and harm</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jonah4:8\">JON 4:8</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps121:6\">PSA 121:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa49:10\">ISA 49:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt13:6\">MAT 13:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas1:11\">JAS 1:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev7:16\">REV 7:16</a></p>\n<h2>Worship of the sun</h2>\n<h3>Forbidden to God's people</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut4:19\">DEU 4:19</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut17:2-Deut17:5\">DEU 17:2–17:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job31:26-Job31:28\">JOB 31:26–31:28</a></p>\n<h3>Practised in Israel and Egypt</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek8:16\">EZK 8:16</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs23:5\">2KI 23:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs23:11\">2KI 23:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer8:1-Jer8:2\">JER 8:1–8:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer43:13\">JER 43:13</a></p>\n<h2>Sunlight and God's judgment</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Joel2:31\">JOL 2:31</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt24:29-Matt24:30\">MAT 24:29–24:30</a></strong> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark13:24\">MRK 13:24</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke21:25-Luke21:26\">LUK 21:25–21:26</a> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod10:21-Exod10:23\">EXO 10:21–10:23</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa13:9-Isa13:10\">ISA 13:9–13:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer4:28\">JER 4:28</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek32:7-Ezek32:8\">EZK 32:7–32:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Joel3:14-Joel3:15\">JOL 3:14–3:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Amos5:20\">AMO 5:20</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt27:45\">MAT 27:45</a> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark15:33\">MRK 15:33</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke23:44\">LUK 23:44</a> <em>the crucifixion</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts2:20\">ACT 2:20</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev6:12-Rev6:17\">REV 6:12–6:17</a></p>\n<h2>God and the sun</h2>\n<h3>God as creator and controller</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job9:7\">JOB 9:7</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps74:16\">PSA 74:16</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Josh10:12-Josh10:13\">JOS 10:12–10:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs20:8-2Kgs20:11\">2KI 20:8–20:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps19:1-Ps19:6\">PSA 19:1–19:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps148:3\">PSA 148:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps148:5\">PSA 148:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa38:8\">ISA 38:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer31:35-Jer31:36\">JER 31:35–31:36</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hab3:11\">HAB 3:11</a></p>\n<h3>God likened to the sun</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke1:78-Luke1:79\">LUK 1:78–1:79</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps84:11\">PSA 84:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa9:2\">ISA 9:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hab3:4\">HAB 3:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mal4:2\">MAL 4:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt17:2\">MAT 17:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor4:6\">2CO 4:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev1:16\">REV 1:16</a></p>\n<h3>God's glory outshines the sun</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev21:23\">REV 21:23</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa24:23\">ISA 24:23</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa60:19-Isa60:20\">ISA 60:19–60:20</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts26:13\">ACT 26:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev22:5\">REV 22:5</a></p>\n<h2>Metaphorical allusions to the sun</h2>\n<h3>In Paul's conversion experience</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts26:13\">ACT 26:13</a></strong></p>\n<h3>As righteousness</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps37:6\">PSA 37:6</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt13:43\">MAT 13:43</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam23:3-2Sam23:4\">2SA 23:3–23:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov4:18\">PRO 4:18</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa58:8\">ISA 58:8</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa58:10\">ISA 58:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa62:1\">ISA 62:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan12:3\">DAN 12:3</a></p>\n<h3>As constancy and dependability</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hos6:3\">HOS 6:3</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps72:5\">PSA 72:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps72:17\">PSA 72:17</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps89:36\">PSA 89:36</a></p>\n<h3>The setting sun signifying a premature end</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer15:9\">JER 15:9</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Amos8:9\">AMO 8:9</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mic3:6\">MIC 3:6</a></p>\n<h2>Miracles and signs concerning the sun</h2>\n<p>Darkening of the sun:\n <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa5:30\">ISA 5:30</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa24:23\">ISA 24:23</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Amos8:9\">AMO 8:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Josh10:12-Josh10:13\">JOS 10:12–10:13</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs20:11\">2KI 20:11</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa38:8\">ISA 38:8</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hab3:11\">HAB 3:11</a></p>",
